Insider Activity


Individual




Charles H. Noski



Mr. Charles H. Noski, CPA, is Chairman at Financial Accounting Foundation, Independent Director at The Priceline Group, Inc., Independent Director at Avon Products, Inc., Independent Director at Microsoft Corp., a Member at The American Institute of Certified Public Accountants, and a Member at Financial Executives International. He is on the Board of Directors at The Priceline Group, Inc., The National Association of Corporate Directors, Inc., Avon Products, Inc., Microsoft Corp., and Performing Arts Center of Los Angeles County.
Mr. Noski was previously employed as Independent Director by Avery Dennison Corp., Vice Chairman by Bank of America Corp., Chief Financial Officer, Director & Vice President by Northrop Grumman Corp., Vice Chairman, Chief Financial Officer & SEVP by AT&T Corp., President, Chief Operating Officer & Director by Hughes Electronics Corp., Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by United Technologies Corp., a Member-Standing Advisory Group by The Public Co. Accounting Oversight Board, and Partner by Deloitte & Touche LLP. He also served on the board at Automatic Data Processing, Inc., Morgan Stanley, Air Products & Chemicals, Inc., Air Products & Chemicals, Inc., Merrill Lynch & Co., Inc., and Teledyne Technologies, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from California State University-Northridge and a graduate degree from California State University-Northridge.



