Noski has been a director of Air Products & Chemicals, Automatic Data Processing, AT&T Corp., Avery Dennison, Morgan Stanley, and Northrop Grumman [2]. He currently serves on the boards of directors of Microsoft [4], Avon Products, and The Priceline Group .
