August 23, 1952 (1952-08-23) (age 64)
Eureka, California


Occupation
CFO of Bank of America


Board member of
Microsoft, Avon Products and The Priceline Group


Spouse(s)
Lisa


Children
2


Charles H. Noski (born August 23, 1952 in Eureka, California[1]) retired from Bank of America, September 1, 2012 .[2]
